# vim-yomikata

![](http://go-gyazo.appspot.com/33d14880a1ec57ac.png)

## Usage

`<leader>y` on the word that you can't read

## Requirements

[yomikata command](https://github.com/mattn/yomikata)

## Installation

```vim
Plug "mattn/vim-yomikata"
```

